snippet.title: Redfall - Bethesda's Pete Hines Talks Arkane's History and Vision | Xbox & Bethesda Showcase 2022
snippet.description:
Bethesda's VP of Marketing Pete Hines discusses Arkane Studios' history and how it's bringing those years of experience to the development of the vampire co-op  RPG Redfall.
